\c 14
\s Vanhu vose vakashata
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Benzi rakati mumwoyo maro, "Mwari haako." Vakaora, vakabata mabasa anonyangadza; Hapana anoita zvakanaka.
\v 2 Jehovha ari kudenga, akatarira pasi kuvana vavanhu, Kuti aone kana akachenjera aripo, Anotsvaka Mwari.
\v 3 Vakatsauka vose, vakasvibiswa pamwechete; Hapana anoita zvakanaka, kunyange nomumwe.
\v 4 Ko vaiti vose vezvakaipa havana zivo here?
\s Ivo vanodya vanhu vangu sezvavanodya chingwa, Vasingadani kuna Jehovha.
\p
\v 5 Vakanga vachitya zvikuru ipapo; Nokuti Mwari anogara parudzi rwavakarurama.
\p
\v 6 Munonyadzisa zano romurombo, Asi Jehovha ndiye utiziro hwake.
\p
\v 7 Dai kuponeswa kwalsiraeri kwaibva paZioni!
\s Kana Jehovha achidzosa vanhu vake pakutapwa,
\s Ipapo Jakobho achafarisisa kwazvo, naIsiraeri achafara.
